{
  "stem": "13063.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they somehow did it in a way that there was no trace of, of, of, of this activity, that there was no smoke or something.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They hid it in such a way that nobody could tell that there was matzah being baked.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And sure enough, I got a little piece of matzah on, on the first-- on the first day of-- on the first Seder night.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And as far as eating, we were eating vegetables and, and, and some potatoes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They was brought especially for those who, who did not want to eat [NON-ENGLISH] on Pesach.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But it was not enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were always hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was, there was always hunger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was always starvation, not enough of anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But this was a feature that I will never forget.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a-- it was a-- an experience, that in 1944, in a concentration camp, to make a matzah.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was so hidden, it was well-camouflaged that nobody found out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yom Kippur was-- it was in 1943 was Yom-- was Yom Kippur, '44 was, yes, '43 and '44.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was still in, in, in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What can I tell you of Yom Kippur-- Rosh Hashanna and Yom Kippur?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were just davening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were just praying and hoping and imploring Hashem should have mercy and not let the remainder of his people be exterminated, be destroyed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think there were a few.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And each one was trying-- was, was crowding on us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, there were just a few.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But most, most of those Jews knew how to-- the, the prayers book by memory, most of them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no. no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a pair of Tefillin in, in the Plaszow ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, in the camp of Plaszow, I had a pair of Tefillin.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
